{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 10,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 371.295,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.601,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Jacob, speak unto you again,",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.781,
      "end": 4.453,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 4.633,
      "end": 7.884,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning this righteous branch of which I have spoken.",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.564,
      "end": 11.443,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, the promises which we have obtained",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 11.623,
      "end": 14.502,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are promises unto us according to the flesh;",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 14.682,
      "end": 17.283,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, as it has been shown unto me",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 17.463,
      "end": 20.621,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that many of our children shall perish in the flesh",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.801,
      "end": 22.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of unbelief,",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 22.514,
      "end": 25.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, God will be merciful unto many;",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 25.713,
      "end": 27.849,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and our children shall be restored,",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 28.029,
      "end": 30.908,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may come to that which will give them",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 31.088,
      "end": 33.642,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the true knowledge of their Redeemer.",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 34.322,
      "end": 36.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, as I said unto you,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 36.452,
      "end": 38.635,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it must needs be expedient that Christ\u2014",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 38.815,
      "end": 43.366,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for in the last night the angel spake unto me that this should be his name\u2014",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 43.546,
      "end": 45.496,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should come among the Jews,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 45.676,
      "end": 48.973,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among those who are the more wicked part of the world;",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 49.153,
      "end": 51.011,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall crucify him\u2014",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 51.191,
      "end": 53.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus it behooveth our God,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 53.647,
      "end": 58.105,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there is none other nation on earth that would crucify their God.",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 58.785,
      "end": 63.057,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For should the mighty miracles be wrought among other nations",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 63.237,
      "end": 66.07,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they would repent, and know that he be their God.",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 66.75,
      "end": 69.629,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But because of priestcrafts and iniquities,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 69.809,
      "end": 73.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they at Jerusalem will stiffen their necks against him,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 73.24,
      "end": 74.68,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he be crucified.",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 75.36,
      "end": 78.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, because of their iniquities,",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 78.28,
      "end": 81.02,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "destructions, famines, pestilences,",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 81.2,
      "end": 83.615,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bloodshed shall come upon them;",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 83.795,
      "end": 85.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they who shall not be destroyed",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 86.065,
      "end": 88.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be scattered among all nations.",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 89.392,
      "end": 91.621,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, thus saith the Lord God:",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 91.801,
      "end": 94.448,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "When the day cometh that they shall believe in me,",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 94.628,
      "end": 96.207,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I am Christ,",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 96.387,
      "end": 99.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then have I covenanted with their fathers",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 99.307,
      "end": 102.651,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall be restored in the flesh, upon the earth,",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 102.831,
      "end": 105.107,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the lands of their inheritance.",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 105.787,
      "end": 109.363,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall come to pass that they shall be gathered in",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 109.543,
      "end": 113.351,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from their long dispersion, from the isles of the sea,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 113.531,
      "end": 115.714,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and from the four parts of the earth;",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 115.894,
      "end": 119.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the nations of the Gentiles shall be great in the eyes of me,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 119.65,
      "end": 120.765,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith God,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 120.945,
      "end": 123.964,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in carrying them forth to the lands of their inheritance.",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 124.644,
      "end": 128.731,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, the kings of the Gentiles shall be nursing fathers unto them,",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 128.911,
      "end": 131.697,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their queens shall become nursing mothers;",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 131.877,
      "end": 136.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the promises of the Lord are great unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 136.376,
      "end": 139.302,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he hath spoken it, and who can dispute?",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 139.982,
      "end": 141.654,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, this land,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 141.834,
      "end": 142.902,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "said God,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 143.082,
      "end": 145.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be a land of thine inheritance,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 145.77,
      "end": 148.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Gentiles shall be blessed upon the land.",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 149.515,
      "end": 153.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And this land shall be a land of liberty unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 153.364,
      "end": 156.15,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there shall be no kings upon the land,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 156.33,
      "end": 158.606,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who shall raise up unto the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 159.286,
      "end": 162.676,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will fortify this land against all other nations.",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 163.356,
      "end": 166.839,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he that fighteth against Zion shall perish, saith God.",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 167.519,
      "end": 170.863,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he that raiseth up a king against me shall perish,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 171.043,
      "end": 172.715,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I, the Lord,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 172.895,
      "end": 174.288,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the king of heaven,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 174.468,
      "end": 175.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will be their king,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 175.995,
      "end": 178.41,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I will be a light unto them forever,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 178.59,
      "end": 180.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that hear my words.",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 180.895,
      "end": 182.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, for this cause,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 182.84,
      "end": 185.162,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that my covenants may be fulfilled",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 185.342,
      "end": 188.593,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have made unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 188.773,
      "end": 191.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I will do unto them while they are in the flesh,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 191.879,
      "end": 194.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I must needs destroy the secret works of darkness,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 195.031,
      "end": 196.471,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of murders,",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 196.651,
      "end": 198.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of abominations.",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 198.956,
      "end": 201.65,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, he that fighteth against Zion,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 201.83,
      "end": 203.548,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both Jew and Gentile,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 203.728,
      "end": 205.493,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both bond and free,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 205.673,
      "end": 207.345,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both male and female,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 207.525,
      "end": 208.825,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall perish;",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 209.005,
      "end": 212.256,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they are they who are the whore of all the earth;",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 212.436,
      "end": 216.198,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they who are not for me are against me, saith our God.",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 216.878,
      "end": 221.801,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I will fulfil my promises which I have made unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 221.981,
      "end": 224.675,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I will do unto them while they are in the flesh\u2014",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 225.355,
      "end": 228.745,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, my beloved brethren, thus saith our God:",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 228.925,
      "end": 231.99,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will afflict thy seed by the hand of the Gentiles;",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 232.17,
      "end": 235.328,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, I will soften the hearts of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 235.508,
      "end": 238.666,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall be like unto a father to them;",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 238.846,
      "end": 241.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the Gentiles shall be blessed",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 241.487,
      "end": 244.227,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and numbered among the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 244.907,
      "end": 248.158,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I will consecrate this land unto thy seed,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 248.338,
      "end": 251.217,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and them who shall be numbered among thy seed,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 251.397,
      "end": 254.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "forever, for the land of their inheritance;",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 254.317,
      "end": 256.221,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it is a choice land,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 256.401,
      "end": 258.026,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith God unto me,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 258.206,
      "end": 260.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "above all other lands,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 260.197,
      "end": 263.541,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore I will have all men that dwell thereon",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 263.721,
      "end": 266.322,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall worship me, saith God.",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 267.002,
      "end": 269.045,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 269.225,
      "end": 272.058,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "seeing that our merciful God has given us",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 272.238,
      "end": 274.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so great knowledge concerning these things,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 275.065,
      "end": 276.365,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "let us remember him,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 276.545,
      "end": 278.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and lay aside our sins,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 278.49,
      "end": 280.301,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and not hang down our heads,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 280.481,
      "end": 282.339,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for we are not cast off;",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 282.519,
      "end": 287.952,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, we have been driven out of the land of our inheritance;",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 288.132,
      "end": 290.547,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but we have been led to a better land,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 290.727,
      "end": 293.421,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Lord has made the sea our path,",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 293.601,
      "end": 296.341,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we are upon an isle of the sea.",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 297.021,
      "end": 299.622,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But great are the promises of the Lord",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 299.802,
      "end": 302.867,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto them who are upon the isles of the sea;",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 303.047,
      "end": 305.09,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore as it says isles,",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 305.27,
      "end": 307.592,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there must needs be more than this,",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 307.772,
      "end": 310.605,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they are inhabited also by our brethren.",
      "verse": "10:21",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 311.285,
      "end": 314.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, the Lord God has led away from time to time",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 314.902,
      "end": 316.899,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 317.079,
      "end": 319.494,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to his will and pleasure.",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 319.674,
      "end": 321.16,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now behold,",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 321.34,
      "end": 324.544,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord remembereth all them who have been broken off,",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 324.724,
      "end": 327.046,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore he remembereth us also.",
      "verse": "10:22",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 327.726,
      "end": 329.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore, cheer up your hearts,",
      "verse": "10:23",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 329.81,
      "end": 332.875,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and remember that ye are free to act for yourselves\u2014",
      "verse": "10:23",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 333.055,
      "end": 337.745,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to choose the way of everlasting death or the way of eternal life.",
      "verse": "10:23",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 338.425,
      "end": 340.375,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 340.555,
      "end": 343.156,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "reconcile yourselves to the will of God,",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 343.336,
      "end": 346.633,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and not to the will of the devil and the flesh;",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 346.813,
      "end": 350.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and remember, after ye are reconciled unto God,",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 350.244,
      "end": 353.913,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it is only in and through the grace of God that ye are saved.",
      "verse": "10:24",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 354.593,
      "end": 359.005,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, may God raise you from death by the power of the resurrection,",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 359.185,
      "end": 363.318,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also from everlasting death by the power of the atonement,",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 363.498,
      "end": 366.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye may be received into the eternal kingdom of God,",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 366.929,
      "end": 369.623,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye may praise him through grace divine.",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 369.803,
      "end": 370.639,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "10:25",
      "lineIndex": 131
    }
  ]
}